{"tid":264101,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打係日本而又想睇波？","createTime":"2017-05-30T14:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T04:42:01.000Z","uid":55989,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fcad82fd12dc1d569de79ee89cc3ba7859eea36f","tid":264101,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:18:05.000Z","msg":"是咁的 小弟早幾日買左張日職既波飛<br />\n唔知係咩杯既分組賽<br />\n清水心跳主場vsFC東京<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.jleague.jp/sp/club/ftokyo/day/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jleague.jp%2Fsp%2Fclub%2Fftokyo%2Fday%2F&d=zwaEkXe1hEW1tFfMBPrTdwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=63f32041\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.jleague.jp/sp/club/ftokyo/day/</a><br />\n31/5 即係聽晚果場<br />\n但因為行程臨時有變所以去唔到睇<br />\n錢就比左了 但唔想浪費 <br />\n有興趣既巴打可以tg小弟 <br />\n我會send條qr quote 比你<br />\n之後你就可以入場睇波<br />\n唯一既條件係 你要好好享受呢場比賽呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nMy TG <a href=\"https://t.me/rondo9999\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Frondo9999&d=zwaEkXe1hEW1tFfMBPrTdwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=5fde254a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/rondo9999</a>"},{"pid":"256598cf2b1d3837436527d84329c64b3565f5e9","tid":264101,"uid":55989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:22:45.000Z","msg":"推一推"},{"pid":"d79b492c52c577e718e0663b808969649de4862d","tid":264101,"uid":799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:23:30.000Z","msg":"幫手推"},{"pid":"f440b4c400adaa100a1d7bf3194d8efe2b8539a0","tid":264101,"uid":70545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T14:24:57.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7070beac4f7860edee18af2e3d47b0ff671e2077","tid":264101,"uid":23783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim